{"tid":1564182,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"台長梁錦祥建議：動用民間力量整理7月到現在無故失蹤自殺名單","createTime":"2019-09-12T16:11:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-13T08:15:09.000Z","uid":4618,"like":15,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"0273fa913a888ea0f24d5ada697b17dafb2c9f0f","tid":1564182,"uid":4618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T16:11:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/tpt6lgKg0tA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Ftpt6lgKg0tA&d=m%2FBV6vIUiVByATU953YnmOdgoykoOisTuuABwIAScok%3D&h=11c67844\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/tpt6lgKg0tA</a><br />\n22:50 <br />\n<br />\n由7月份以來，佢地無故失蹤、變咗浮屍，每個人都要列返個人名同背景出嚟。<br />\n<br />\n我地將來或者稍後係要動用民間資源，<span style=\"color: red;\">每個人都要double check 究竟呢個人有冇參與過示威行動，佢呢一排大概去過邊到。</span><br />\n<br />\n呢個聽落好似好難，<span style=\"color: red;\">但如果大家一齊去做呢，你總會搵到一啲喺佢地身邊熟悉嘅人，親戚也好朋友也好。</span>因為依家最奇怪一件事就係，呢啲人死咗好似冇家庭㗎。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">你要去逐個逐個case去摸，你唔好怕長時間，因為就算事後一段時間之後，你總會搵到佢家人朋友，一定會搵到一啲小小嘅線索</span>，就係曾經佢地有冇被捕，或者警方曾經接觸過佢地。但當然依家最緊急就係嗰三個人。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">仲有就係因為依家仲有少少片出嚟，啲片本身match唔match到依家失蹤嘅人。</span>起底嗰啲人係可以做到呢樣嘢，你唔一定要做足，但個別嘅人有高度懷疑嘅，以依家能力係做得到。<br />\n<br />\n所以我覺得可能等多一兩日，睇下啲片陸續出嚟，睇下可唔可以搵到啲人發動去做呢樣嘢。"},{"pid":"a2114457ba3f4e59c37dec0262f3d0bf484bda38","tid":1564182,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T16:12:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"82851fe91880fd3fd57de202017db5eabf501c44","tid":1564182,"uid":4618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T16:18:55.000Z","msg":"有冇起底組做緊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49facfd419519c1d27813d89fbe7f068ad93acf6","tid":1564182,"uid":34047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T16:25:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7bd30b4880fed2f48026b35140302c0ef58040df","tid":1564182,"uid":258731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0273fa913a888ea0f24d5ada697b17dafb2c9f0f","tid":1564182,"uid":4618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T16:11:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/tpt6lgKg0tA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Ftpt6lgKg0tA&d=m%2FBV6vIUiVByATU953YnmOdgoykoOisTuuABwIAScok%3D&h=11c67844\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/tpt6lgKg0tA</a><br />\n22:50 <br />\n<br />\n由7月份以來，佢地無故失蹤、變咗浮屍，每個人都要列返個人名同背景出嚟。<br />\n<br />\n我地將來或者稍後係要動用民間資源，<span style=\"color: red;\">每個人都要double check 究竟呢個人有冇參與過示威行動，佢呢一排大概去過邊到。</span><br />\n<br />\n呢個聽落好似好難，<span style=\"color: red;\">但如果大家一齊去做呢，你總會搵到一啲喺佢地身邊熟悉嘅人，親戚也好朋友也好。</span>因為依家最奇怪一件事就係，呢啲人死咗好似冇家庭㗎。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">你要去逐個逐個case去摸，你唔好怕長時間，因為就算事後一段時間之後，你總會搵到佢家人朋友，一定會搵到一啲小小嘅線索</span>，就係曾經佢地有冇被捕，或者警方曾經接觸過佢地。但當然依家最緊急就係嗰三個人。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">仲有就係因為依家仲有少少片出嚟，啲片本身match唔match到依家失蹤嘅人。</span>起底嗰啲人係可以做到呢樣嘢，你唔一定要做足，但個別嘅人有高度懷疑嘅，以依家能力係做得到。<br />\n<br />\n所以我覺得可能等多一兩日，睇下啲片陸續出嚟，睇下可唔可以搵到啲人發動去做呢樣嘢。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T16:25:42.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">海外臨時政府 自由香港<br />\nFREE HONG KONG</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/nBMTNBB.jpg\" data-th